  <body>
   <p><placeName ref="cwgk:P00004898">Owensboro</placeName>' <placeName ref="cwgk:P001800">Ky</placeName>. <date when="1864-05-19">May 19<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 64</date>
<lb/>Hon. <persName ref="cwgk:N001000">Thomas. E. Bramlett</persName>
<lb/>D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Sir-</p>
   <p>Permit us the pleasure of introducing to you our young friend <persName ref="cwgk:N00013848">Robert Allen</persName> -- He has been in the <orgName ref="cwgk:O00001186">service of his Country</orgName>, and was a member and officer in the "<orgName ref="cwgk:O00002664">17<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Ky</orgName>" but owing to sickness was honorably discharged -- Having recovered his strength, he looks to the war path again and visits <placeName ref="cwgk:P00000308">Frankfort</placeName> to consult our patriotic Governor as to the best place for him to fill in maintaining <orgName ref="cwgk:O00002945">our glorious Country</orgName> -- </p>
<p>We hope you will aid him in his purpose -- </p>
<p>Truly your friends
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00013862">W. Anthony</persName>
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00013861">W<hi rend="sup">m</hi> B Wall</persName>
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00013849">J. W. Compton</persName>
<lb/>Surgeon <orgName ref="cwgk:O00012894">Brd Enrolment</orgName> <orgName ref="cwgk:O00003024">2<hi rend="sup">nd</hi> Dist</orgName> Ky
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00013860">N B Allen</persName> Com<hi rend="sup">r</hi>. Brd.
<lb/>Enrolment 2<hi rend="sup">d</hi> Dist
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00001837">John R Grissom</persName> Ky.
<lb/>Pro Mar 2nd
<lb/>Dist Ky<pb/></p>
<p>Owensboro Ky
<lb/><date when="1864-05-19">May 19<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> 1864</date><figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Allen Robert
<lb/>Athony W } &amp; others<figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Recommending M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Robert Allen to your favorable consideration He is desirous to assist the Governor in raising the 10.000 six months men.<figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Recruiting authority issued &amp; delivered <date when="1864-05-23">23<hi rend="sup">d</hi> May 1864</date><figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Rec<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">d</hi></hi> <orgName ref="cwgk:O00000388">A G O.</orgName> <date when="1864-05-23">23<hi rend="sup">d</hi> May 1864</date></p>
